{"tid":896246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【加國巴打睇路】比亞迪電動的士進軍加拿大","createTime":"2018-11-10T00:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T01:35:03.000Z","uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5065ecfa8578f3bd0fb7b180c6f4119bb3b26b5","tid":896246,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"中國品牌比亞迪（BYD）電動車E6，即將進軍加拿大，預料明年初後將會在街頭上看到它們的蹤影，滿地可甚至會有電動的士可搭。<br />\n<br />\n據指，比亞迪正在對E6進行調整，以配合加拿大汽車安全及充電標準。魁北克電動車協會（AVEQ）表示，明年在滿地可將會出現一間新的士公司，專門用比亞迪的汽車，包括E6來提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中國製造的電池安全性，近年受到批評。電動車專家Matthew Klippenstein表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">很多中國製造汽車的安全標準，未必達到歐洲及北美標準</span>，但它們賣得便宜，在發展中國家市場如印尼和巴西等較具優勢，北美和歐洲汽車的售價難與其競爭。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得鼓勵愛國加籍華人坐多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17ac73559b499f88fe342420fca6e904a97aa5b","tid":896246,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:08:56.000Z","msg":"e6深圳坐過，好靜，加速好快"},{"pid":"03e04e242158c6ccce796a9ab5f602500d454a77","tid":896246,"uid":57376,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d17ac73559b499f88fe342420fca6e904a97aa5b","tid":896246,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:08:56.000Z","msg":"e6深圳坐過，好靜，加速好快"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:13:04.000Z","msg":"爆炸都好靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c484b870356c3d6e8a78a7fff4ac626ab9cd917f","tid":896246,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:14:37.000Z","msg":"中屬北美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905754716f6105eb9a4c4f5b597c63f5ce093eee","tid":896246,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T00:16:58.000Z","msg":"愛國加籍華人：我地自己有車，不了，留返畀黎旅行嘅愛國同胞同港豬坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d